{"tid":374650,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大件事冇人講，HL劇本製作人Marc Laidlaw公開HL3劇本","createTime":"2017-08-26T02:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T03:18:12.000Z","uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3928f034c819cd98d99852c15e960502d56a9a","tid":374650,"uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://www.marclaidlaw.com/epistle-3//[url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.marclaidlaw.com%2Fepistle-3%2F%2F%5Burl%5D&d=yrJc84O7XcVjWbJJagXf9m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1a31d256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.marclaidlaw.com/epistle-3//[url]</a><br />\n<br />\n事源係Valve睇黎完全冇意向去整HL3，只係想專注整steam同多人遊戲（CSGO/DOTA)而且當年HL團隊都各散東西，Marc Laidlaw覺得HL3已經不可能發生所以放劇本出黎。<br />\n<br />\n劇本尾段係Marc Laidlaw既獨白<br />\n &quot;Old friends have been silenced, or fallen by the wayside. I no longer know or recognize most members of the research team, though I believe the spirit of rebellion still persists. I expect you know better than I the appropriate course of action, and I leave you to it. Expect no further correspondence from me regarding these matters; this is my final episode.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nHL3 confirmed... to be officially dead."},{"pid":"90f076745db816ab26000b482642ce92d58baa9b","tid":374650,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"佢已經帶哂頭盔話fan fic <br />\n最後一段好明顯寫比valve 睇<br />\n<br />\nValve 正宗食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b8cfb6dc1a4e6a683d065fd165fa1ae2f6a0c3","tid":374650,"uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢已經帶哂頭盔話fan fic <br />\n最後一段好明顯寫比valve 睇<br />\n<br />\nValve 正宗食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎Valve真係冇打算繼續開發單人遊戲，只係想食住steam同Multiplayer，In game purchase條水。<br />\n昔日神作HL Portal已成歷史，HL3永遠都唔會有，Valve真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84be1e3f9faa3563ef55a68b0357bdb0835aa6c4","tid":374650,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"唔係episode 3咩"},{"pid":"a80d7ee57c60748f08581b3052adfbbb15b21aab","tid":374650,"uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係episode 3咩</blockquote><br />\n其實係，不過d人叫開HL3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a345a9c2a0868b5b70946eda151172369bc5d8","tid":374650,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係episode 3咩</blockquote><br />\n其實係，不過d人叫開HL3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴晚睇左，年頭吹到話JJ會開Half Life電影<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時話cut EP3 直接出埋3嫁嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話個故事一早作定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家搞到咁，佢都未必想出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}